#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A hand-made bow made that has been very carefully decorated and painted. "
"It's more a costume accessory than a deadly weapon."
msgstr "一把手工制作的弓，经过精心装饰和涂装。它更像是一件服装配饰，而非致命武器。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Bow Mk1"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Bow Mk1s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制弓 Mk1"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A handcrafted bow assembled with an experienced hand, from scavenged "
"materials."
msgstr "一把由经验丰富的手艺人用拾荒材料组装而成的手工弓。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Bow Mk2"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Bow Mk2s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制弓 Mk2"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"It is an improved version of the Cutie Custom Bow Mk1. The performance "
"improved greatly by reinforcing the frame with steel, but consequently is "
"larger and heavier than its predecessor"
msgstr "这是可爱定制弓 Mk1 的改进版。通过用钢材加固框架，性能大幅提升，但因此比前代更大更重。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Bow Mk3"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Bow Mk3s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制弓 Mk3"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"It is an improved version of the Cutie Custom Bow Mk2. The frame has been "
"made even larger and reinforced with higher quality materials than its "
"predecessor. Consequently, it is an excellent bow that looks like it was "
"made by a master craftsman."
msgstr "这是可爱定制弓 Mk2 的改进版。框架变得更大，并用更高质量的材料加固。因此，它是一把看起来像由大师工匠制作的优秀弓。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Shieldbow"
msgid_plural "Cute Shieldbows"
msgstr[0] "可爱盾弓"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"This is a very heavy bow with a sharp steel spike protruding from the front."
" It's much harder to shoot accurately, but can endure close combat much "
"better than regular bows."
msgstr "这是一把非常重的弓，前端伸出锋利的钢刺。它更难精准射击，但比普通弓更能承受近战。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Shelia (blade form)"
msgid_plural "Cute Shelia (blade form)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱希莉娅（刀刃形态）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Cute Shelia (blade form)'}.
#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Transform weapon"
msgstr "变形武器"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Cute Shelia (blade form)'}.
#: .\weapon.json
msgid "The Shelia expands into its bow form."
msgstr "希莉娅展开为弓形态。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Shelia (blade form)'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"This device is a complex transforming weapon capable of becoming either a "
"bladed melee weapon, or a powerful bow. This is the first release in the "
"[Cute Combat] series of of stylish protective equipment by the world's "
"leading maid fashion brand Alice & Maria. The weapon itself proved to be "
"quite desirable, as it could transform for engaging foes at both long range "
"and in close combat. However, it ended up earning the nickname 'Nighmarish "
"Shelia' due to its overly complex design making it too expensive for the "
"mass market, and bankrupting its designer."
msgstr ""
"该装置是一种复杂的变形武器，既能变为刀刃近战武器，也能变为强力弓。这是世界领先的女仆时尚品牌爱丽丝与玛丽亚推出的时尚防护装备系列【可爱战斗】的首款产品。该武器本身被证明相当受欢迎，因为它能变形以应对远程和近战的敌人。然而，由于其设计过于复杂，导致大规模生产成本过高，并使设计师破产，最终赢得了“噩梦希莉娅”的绰号。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Shelia (bow form)"
msgid_plural "Cute Shelia (bow form)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱希莉娅（弓形态）"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Lelia"
msgid_plural "Cute Lelias"
msgstr[0] "可爱蕾莉娅"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"An elegant bow decorated with angelic feathers at each end, and possessing a"
" strong metal handguard. This is the second product in the series of "
"fashionable self-defense tools [Cute Combat] series revealed by the world's "
"leading maid fashion brand Alice & Maria. The material used for the metal "
"plate was announced at the same time as the same product, it was expected to"
" be a next generation alloy that possesses flexibility and durability "
"despite being very light, but it was too expensive to mass produce. "
"Consequently this weapon only sold a limited number."
msgstr ""
"一把优雅的弓，两端装饰有天使羽毛，并配有坚固的金属护手。这是世界领先的女仆时尚品牌爱丽丝与玛丽亚推出的时尚自卫工具系列【可爱战斗】的第二款产品。用于金属板的材料与产品同时公布，它被期望成为一种兼具柔韧性和耐用性的轻质下一代合金，但大规模生产成本过高。因此，该武器仅限量销售。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Daikyu"
msgid_plural "Cute Daikyus"
msgstr[0] "可爱大弓"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"The daikyu is the traditional Japanese equivalent of the longbow. It's a "
"complex weapon to master, but has enough power to penetrate even the "
"heaviest armor."
msgstr "大弓是日本传统的长弓。它是一种难以掌握的复杂武器，但拥有足以穿透最重装甲的威力。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Glass Bow"
msgid_plural "Cute Glass Bows"
msgstr[0] "可爱玻璃弓"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A heavy translucent glass bow, made possible due to the integration of "
"carbom nanotubes into its structure."
msgstr "一把沉重的半透明玻璃弓，通过在其结构中集成碳纳米管得以实现。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Rita and Rosa (defence mode)"
msgid_plural "Cute Rita and Rosa (defence mode)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱丽塔与罗莎（防御模式）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Cute Rita and Rosa (defence mode)'}.
