#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Cute Twin Crystals (polearm form)'}.
#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Switch to twin blade form"
msgstr "切换至双剑形态"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Cute Twin Crystals (polearm form)'}.
#: .\weapon.json
msgid "You seperate the polarm into two blades"
msgstr "你将长柄武器拆分为两把剑刃。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Twin Crystals (polearm form)'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A two-ended polearm composed of beautifully crystalline swords attached "
"together at the hilt."
msgstr "一柄双头长柄武器，由美丽的晶化剑刃在剑柄处连接而成。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Twin Crystals Prototype"
msgid_plural "Cute Twin Crystals Prototypes"
msgstr[0] "可爱双晶原型"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Twin Crystals Prototype'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A beautiful two-ended polearm with beautiful crystalline blades... though it"
" seems pretty fragile."
msgstr "一柄美丽的双头长柄武器，配有美丽的晶化剑刃……不过看起来相当脆弱。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Spear (Ver.1)"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Spear (Ver.1)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制长矛（版本1）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Custom Spear (Ver.1)'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A rusty spear made from a piece of steel. Despite being cheap, it still "
"allows you to keep your distance from the undead."
msgstr "一把由钢材制成的生锈长矛。尽管廉价，它仍能让你与不死生物保持距离。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Spear (Ver.2)"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Spear (Ver.2)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制长矛（版本2）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Custom Spear (Ver.2)'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"An improved version of the Custom Spear (Ver.1). A practical, easy to use "
"weapon, the rust has been removed with a piece of glass and careful "
"polishing. In addition, the grip has been reinforced for increased "
"durability."
msgstr "定制长矛（版本1）的改进版。一把实用、易用的武器，锈迹已用玻璃片仔细打磨去除。此外，握柄经过加固以增加耐久度。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Custom Spear(Ver.3)"
msgid_plural "Cute Custom Spear(Ver.3)s"
msgstr[0] "可爱定制长矛（版本3）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Custom Spear(Ver.3)'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"An improved version of the Custom Spear (Ver.2). The tip has been further "
"sharpened and reinforced, increasing its range and killing ability. An "
"improved hand guard allows for greater effectiveness at close-range. A blue "
"ribbon has been attached to it."
msgstr "定制长矛（版本2）的改进版。矛尖经过进一步锐化和加固，增加了攻击范围和杀伤力。改进的护手使其在近战时更有效。上面系有一条蓝色丝带。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Kitchen Knives"
msgid_plural "Cute Kitchen Knivess"
msgstr[0] "可爱厨房刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Kitchen Knives'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"Rather than a knife and fork set, this a pair of knives. It may not be "
"proper etiquette at the table, but it's proper etiquette in combat."
msgstr "这不是一套刀叉，而是一对刀。在餐桌上可能不合礼仪，但在战斗中却是得体的规矩。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Improvised Short Sword"
msgid_plural "Cute Improvised Short Swords"
msgstr[0] "可爱临时短剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Improvised Short Sword'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A quality handmade short sword. Probably the best that could be done without"
" proper smithing tools."
msgstr "一把优质的手工短剑。在没有适当锻造工具的情况下，这可能是能做到的最好作品。"

#: .\weapon.json
msgid "Cute Barlance"
msgid_plural "Cute Barlances"
msgstr[0] "可爱撬棍长枪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Barlance'}
#: .\weapon.json
msgid ""
"A lance composed of multiple crowbars made of Alice and Maria's proprietary "
"advanced alloy. Crude, but functional."
msgstr "一柄由多根爱丽丝与玛丽亚专利先进合金制成的撬棍组成的长枪。粗糙，但实用。"

